high_descs: Turn to the left and move to the black cocktail table.
Pick up the white tea pot that is closest to you on the table.
Turn around and move toward the table with the large brown box.
Put the tea pot on the table.
Turn around and go back to the black cocktail table.
Pick up the other white tea pot on the table.
Move across the room to the low table with the big brown box.
Put the tea pot down on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and face the coffee table.
Pick up the watering can on the coffee table.
Turn right.  Move towards the wall.  Turn right and face the table.
Put the watering can down on the table.  To the right of the black figurine.
Turn around and go towards the wall. Turn left in front of the tv and move to the coffee table.  Face the coffee table.
Pick up the watering can on the table.
Turn left and move to the wall.  Turn right and go to the table.
Put the watering can down on the left corner of the table.

grab the white water spout off of the table
turn around and walk over to the black cabinet on the floor
place the water spout on top of the black cabinet
